Check the rankings of Korean actors, singers, and entertainers at once.
Share pictures, GIFs, videos and solving Korean entertainment quizzes!
Communicate with the fandom in Chat Room!

[⏰Check out the rankings at a glance! Real-time voting every day]
- Vote hearts to your bias and make your bias No.1!
- Real-time rankings that you can check out at a glance.
- The rankings are renewed every day! Come and vote every day!

[💎Support Event for bias!]
- Get your fandom together and gift your bias with ads for their special anniversaries!
- Complete the fundraising of the support event to give ads to celebs.

🎓I'm a big fan of Korean Celebs! “Entertainment Quiz”
Not only solving the quizzes, but also creating a quiz about your celeb!
Test how much you know about Korean Entertainment.

[📅Celeb Schedule]
You can write in and share your celeb's schedule.
Share the schedule of your celeb with your fandom, and get a push notification!

💬Real-Time Chat “Chat Room”
- Create a chat room to chat with fans around the world

🌠My favorite photos of my bias on my phone! “Wallpaper”
- Collect and save your favorite celeb's wallpaper-sized photos from the community at a glance!

🖼Bannergram customized by fans
- If square photo becomes #1 post with the most hearts, the photo will become your celeb's profile photo!
- The 1st, 2nd, 3rd square photos will become the community's bannergram.
- Create your own bannergram to customize your bias community and support your bias.

[🏆Hall of Fame]
- Make your celeb rank higher every day and make them be on Hall of Fame.
